location.fullValue: 885 S Grand Mesa Dr UNIT B

data.description: Well built ranch style home on .29 acres with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, plus a single car garage.  Solar panels were installed in 2020 to provide more energy efficient heating.  Newer laminate flooring throughout.  Separate 24'4" x 10'10" room off the kitchen which would be perfect as a play room, game room or extra living area.  Could also be used as a 4th bedroom, but it has no closet!  Large living room with a wood fireplace.  Covered patio in the back with views of the Grand Mesa which is the largest flat top mesa in the world with over 300+- lakes.  Close to downtown Cedaredge and all amenities including the Grand Mesa Art Center.  Two storage sheds in a fenced in area that would be perfect for a garden.  New stainless steel wall oven just installed!
